                       java.lang.String tags)
        Create a new instance.
        Parameters:
        ltpId - the LTP ID of the file
        fileName - the name of the file
        lastModified - the time when the file was last modified, measured in milliseconds since January 1, 1970, GMT
        fileDescription - an (optional) description about the file. This can also be an empty string.
        tags - a pipe ("|") separated list of tags
